metadata.description:
MEGAMI#09651_2nd Art

[A STORTY]

Her name is MaiMai.

A death Goddess but does not good at death work yet.
Just because her kindness and healing power, too much people told her"It is better to be an angle for you.You do not fit death OK?Kindness is not use for death or healing power."

But she love spirits and enjoy darkness.
When you do love something but you do not really good at that yet, will you give up?

MaiMai never give up!

Hold our love and challenge one more time.
Just like MaiMai.
